Text.defaultText: First of all, you need a pwoper tool in oudew to squab say wubbaw duck. Cwap tsay wubbaw duck squabbaw now.
In fwont of you tseir is a dirty dirty wubbaw duck. Hit it whiz say wubbaw duck squabbaw to make it squeaky clean.
Fuck a duck! Youw tsay best wubbay duck squabber I've ever seen!
Moin moin, I am tsay ducktow, and today we'll learn tsay pwoper way to squab a wubber duck.
